ENTRY            M0068   20260106   20260226   20260226       M143
SUBENT        M0068001   20260106   20260226   20260226       M143
BIB                 11         25
TITLE      Investigation of electrofission of the uranium
           isotopes.
AUTHOR     (V.P.Likhachev,A.Yu.Buki,Yu.V.Vladimirov,
           A.A.Nemashkalo,S.A.Pashchuk,G.A.Savitskiy,
           V.I.Trotsenko,V.A.Fartushny,V.B.Shostak,N.M.Tkach)
REFERENCE  (J,UFZ,27,1456,1982)
INSTITUTE  (4UKRKFT)
FACILITY   (LINAC,4UKRKFT)
METHOD     (EXTB,SITA)
SAMPLE     Specially enriched (~98%) targets of the U-233, U-235,
            U-236 and U-238 isotopes were obtained by vacuum
            evaporation on thin aluminum foils. The thickness of
            the targets (100 - 200 micro-g/cm2) was determined
            by alpha-particle spectrometry.
DETECTOR   (SIBAR)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical errors only.
COMMENT    Results of cross section measurements for the (e,f) -
            reaction on  U-233,235,236,238  nuclei  and  for the
            (e,e'f) reaction of the 238-U nucleus are given.
HISTORY    (19840125C)
           (19910202A) Corrected by V.Varlamov, V.Mclane.
           (20180206U) Corrected by SD and VV: Updated to new
            date formats, lower case, information update, SAMPLE
            added, Ref. corrected, STATUS, PART-DET.
           (20260106U) Corrected by VV and SD: STATUS.
ENDBIB              25
